data.description: OH MY!! you will not believe this incredible home!! Located just 1 mile SE of Byers Co. on 45 acres of country heaven. With easy commute to the metro area this home offers 3 levels plus a loft. an original green home. 4 levels of southern facing glass encompass a solarium offering a vacation style environment overlooking what would be a pond/garden private area. Each of the 3 floors provide single family independent living or ideal for extended family or friends.  The loft is unique in itself. The spiral stairway tops off the masterful design of this remarkable dwelling. Included is a large outbuilding ideal for RV storage, hot rod shop, or whatever you have in mind. Ground floor master makes it easy to come in, take off your boots and enjoy the fruits of your efforts when you kick back and realize this is where you belong. All this for a price that will make you feel the deal.  There are too many features to list in these remarks so this is a must see.
